  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Geneva Study Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cverse2",
        "text": "And David sent and enquired after the woman. And one said, Is not this Bathsheba, the daughter of Eliam, the wife of Uriah the {c} Hittite?",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "And David sent and enquired after the woman. And ",
